ligacao_pcnfsaid_pcmov0.criterios: PCMOV.NUMTRANSVENDA = PCNFSAID.NUMTRANSVENDA and PCNFSAID.DTCANCEL IS NULL

ligacao_pcnfsaid_pccfo0.criterios: PCCFO.CODFISCAL = PCMOV.CODFISCAL and pccfo.codfiscal not between 5300 and 5359 /*prestacao de servico*/ and pccfo.codfiscal not between 5550 and 5603 /*operacoes com ativo imobilizado e credicms*/ and pccfo.codfiscal not between 5926 and 5933 /*operacoes de prest serv e baixas est*/ and pccfo.codfiscal not in (5117,6353,6551,6932) /*servicos ativo ent fut*/ AND nvl(lower(TRIM(pccfo.codoper) ),'x') IN (lower('s'))

ligacao_pcnfent_pcmov0.criterios: PCMOV.NUMTRANSENT = PCNFENT.NUMTRANSENT and PCNFENT.DTCANCEL IS NULL AND NVL(PCMOV.NUMPED,0) = 0

ligacao_pcnfent_pccfo0.criterios: pccfo.codfiscal = pcmov.codfiscal AND pccfo.codfiscal NOT BETWEEN 1500 AND 1554 AND pccfo.codfiscal NOT BETWEEN 1664 AND 1925 AND pccfo.codfiscal NOT BETWEEN 5926 AND 5933 AND pccfo.codfiscal NOT IN (1414,1415,1450,1451,1452,2414,2415,2097,3553) AND nvl(lower(TRIM(pccfo.codoper)), 'x') IN (lower('ed'))

ligacao_sjdcamposis_sjdligcamposis_avuls.criterios: SJDCAMPOSIS.CODCAMPOSIS = SJDLIGCAMPOSIS.CODCAMPOSIS AND lower(trim(SJDLIGCAMPOSIS.CRITERIO_USO)) = lower(trim('campo avulso'))

ligacao_valoressaida_pccidade0.criterios: lower(trim(CIDADE.NOMECIDADE)) = lower(trim(__ALIASTABELA1__.NOMECIDADE)) AND lower(trim(__ALIASTABELA1__.UFCLIENTE)) = lower(trim(CIDADE.UFCIDADE)) and lower(trim(CIDADE.UFCIDADE)) in ('pr','sp','ms')
